#Install Terraform
##Windows
Install Terraform from the Downloads [https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install]
(or)
Use GitHub Codespaces (Free for 60 hours per month)
Login to your GitHub account
Click on the Profile Icon at the top right
Click on "your codespaces" as shown in the 
Codespaces will provide you with a virtual machine with Ubuntu and VS Code by default.
Follow the steps provided on the Downloads [https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install] for Linux.

#Linux
Follow the steps provided on the Downloads [https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install] for Linux.
#macOS
Follow the steps provided on the Downloads [https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install] for macOS.
